{
  "stem": "19210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Akko. ?] And he, he was killed on the spot by one of the, the Arabs guards, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so-- but then what happens was on, on this Haifa-Beirut highway, the main highway, the, the-- my friend, Moshe Sheineman, was working part-time at the telephone company in, in Nahariya.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he caught some kind of conversation that was a little bit strange to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He spoke Arabic, Yiddish, and English, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow another, the Haganah was waiting for-- there was the word that a Transjordan army convoy was coming from Lebanon to their main station in [INAUDIBLE] Carmel in Haifa.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a Transjordan army, army camp there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they did not know when.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So one time, apparently Shalom Sheineman heard this conversation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somebody called.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they notified the, the-- our commander.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, of course, they evacuated several homes near Kiryat Motzkin and Kiryat Haim.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the houses near the main highway were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they, they brought in this time the Palmach, the commanders of the Haganah-- very, very well-trained, super fighters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were there for several days until, ultimately, here comes the Transjordan army convoy-- several trucks, cars, full with arms and ammunitions, with machine guns on the top, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They used to travel like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They liked that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had-- at that time, I was, I was on my way to Nahariya to the meeting place in Kiryat Motzkin, where the convoy congregates.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I never made it there, maybe within a couple of kilometers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All of a sudden, there was these huge explosions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What happened-- one of the Palmach fighters by the name of it [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Uzi-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Uzi ?] was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't remember his family name.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
